primary.context: Caller wanted to pay $1296.17 via credit card
primary.detail: The agent successfully verified the account and confirmed sending the payment link.

secondary.context: Caller wanted to change contact information
secondary.detail: The agent correctly identified the request as out of scope and transferred the caller to the concierge department.

steps: Caller initially requested an agent and was placed in a 20-minute queue.
After the queue failed to provide a human, the AI re-engaged.
Caller requested to make a payment.
AI performed account lookup and identity verification (name, state).
AI confirmed balance and contact details, then initiated the payment link send.
Caller requested to update their phone number.
AI transferred the caller to concierge for the account update.

actions.detail: Initial transfer attempt timed out after 25 minutes in queue.
Looked up account via phone number 4032398855.
Verified name Randy Law and state Alberta.
Transferred to concierge for phone number update.

insights.summary: The caller initially wanted an agent but eventually used the AI to successfully receive a payment link after a long wait in the initial queue. A secondary request to update a phone number was correctly transferred.
insights.verbatim: I'm working on your payment link now. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
